title: Did not receive MSI 2017 Fandom rewards
body: I bought the CBLOL Icon and played games with it during MSI. I didn't get anything, like the promised winners icon and the IP Boost.

replies.body:
Esports rewards take a bit to show up in your account! We'll be distributing them before long and updating players when they do make there way out to you!

 {{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}}
